snippet.title: Dragon Age Inquisition DLC Trailer - Jaws of Hakkon Trailer
snippet.description:
Dragon Age Inquisition DLC Jaws of Hakkon is out now on Xbox One and PC. Get the gist of this story DLC in this new trailer, which promises you will explore a lost chapter of the history of the Inquisition, battle a new dragon, and discover the fate of the last Inquisitor. 

---
